# Agent Proxy App

Lightweight Node.js app that serves as both:
- **Frontend** (simple beige-pink UI in `/public/index.html`)
- **Proxy server** to OpenAI API (hides API key in Replit Secrets)

## Features
- Run local agent loops (A / B / Judge roles)
- Proxy `/v1/responses` requests through Express
- Secure key storage via environment variable `OPENAI_API_KEY`
- Ready to deploy on [Replit](https://replit.com) or GitHub Pages + server

## Quick start
1. Clone repo or import into [Replit](https://replit.com).
2. Add secret `OPENAI_API_KEY` in Replit Secrets.
3. Press **Run**.  
   - Server runs on port `3000`.  
   - Public UI available at `https://<your-repl>.repl.co`.  

